{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1305/comments/4055239.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:None..None?path=gazebo%2Fgui%2FInsertModelWidget.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1305/_/diff#comment-4055239"}}, "parent": {"id": 4054995, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1305/comments/4054995.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1305/_/diff#comment-4054995"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1305, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1305.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1305"}}, "title": "Update InsertModelWidget using SystemPaths::AddModelPathsUpdate"}, "content": {"raw": "That would work too but I would do it at the beginning of the methods that can be executed concurrently and access to shared data (`OnDirectoryChanged()`, `OnModelUpdateRequest()`, Update()`, `OnModelSelection()?`\n\nIn the future, if you add more code that accesses share data in `OnDirectoryChanged()` or `OnModelUpdateRequest()` you might have a race condition.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>That would work too but I would do it at the beginning of the methods that can be executed concurrently and access to shared data (<code>OnDirectoryChanged()</code>, <code>OnModelUpdateRequest()</code>, Update()<code>,</code>OnModelSelection()?`</p>\n<p>In the future, if you add more code that accesses share data in <code>OnDirectoryChanged()</code> or <code>OnModelUpdateRequest()</code> you might have a race condition.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-11-26T22:05:53.415676+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Carlos Ag\u00fcero", "uuid": "{da8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bda8a8e89-